# Design System

Canonical reference: **`DESIGN.md`**

## Typography (from codebase)
- Serif display: Cormorant Garamond, Fraunces
- Sans UI: Inter
- Hand accent: La Belle Aurore (letters only)

## CTAs
- Homepage: `.qbtn`, `.qlink` — quiet, uppercase sans, no shouty buttons
- Chapter: `.btn--primary` with label/hover layers

## Motion
Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`. GSAP pins on homepage — do not break pin init order.

## Imagery
Editorial, atmospheric, Afro-Mediterranean — not stock luxury clichés.

Update DESIGN.md when a durable visual rule emerges.
